headline: Gold and Silver Prices Jump
summary: Gold and silver prices leapt, extending a stretch of extreme volatility.  Gold gained more than 6% to about $4,944 a troy ounce, based on prices for most active futures contracts.   Equivalent contracts for silver added 13% to trade at roughly $87 an ounce.
